data.description: Rarely available, this lovely 2/2 villa in East Lake Woodlands is sure to be a favorite on your list! Nestled in the quiet streets of Quail Forest Cluster Homes, this home has been updated with newer light fixtures, stainless Whirlpool appliances, LVP flooring in the master bed and bathroom, walk in jetted tub, all new impact windows and exterior sliders, and updated bathroom vanities. This split plan home is well laid out with two en-suite bathrooms both with access to the sun room.  Enjoy plenty of living space in the living / dining room space in the center of the home. The sun room on the back of the home has been fully converted from screens and old windows to floor to ceiling impact resistant windows and door. Enjoy additional climate controlled living space with the privacy and amazing views of the fabulous trees and woods. Experience stunning sunsets on your spacious front porch while grilling your favorite foods while enjoying a cool beverage. Equipped with a full sized GE washer and dryer with platforms, laundry won’t be a chore. The wet bar with upper and lower cabinets is great for extra storage and will be a favorite space to entertain! Quail Forest is adjacent to the shopping and restaurants, all without leaving the gated community. The heated pool and social area is just a two minute walk. Enjoy this golfing community that features a country club and restaurant (with additional membership). Your covered parking space is directly in front of your home, and mail boxes sit directly in front of the building. Additional walk-in closet to store your outdoor tools, paint etc. is located in the sun room.  This home is light and bright and so much more! Schedule your private showing today before it’s gone!
